SpringBoot2.x

This application demonstrate different aspect of spring boot2.x:
	1. configure application with spring boot
	2. configure application with log4j2.xml
	3. configure embeded tomcat with seperate port




Note:
	1. load log4j2.xml file from location other than default location:
		java -Dlogging.config='/path/to/log4j2.xml' -jar spring-boot-demo.jar
		
	2. To run your tomcat server on specific port	
		java  -Dserver.port=8888 -jar spring-boot-demo.jar
	3. To load configuration from seperate properties file:
		java -jar spring-boot-demo.jar --spring.config.location=classpath:/conf/demo.properties